data.name: sqlDebtByCustomer.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT person.person_id, person.full_name, ticket.ticket_id, ticket.ticket_date, ticket.description, ticket.comments, ticket.amount, ticket.paid, service_note.service_note_id, service_note.service_note_date, ticket.amount - ticket.paid AS debt, healthcare_company.name AS company_name FROM ticket INNER JOIN service_note ON ticket.service_note_id = service_note.service_note_id INNER JOIN person ON service_note.person_id = person.person_id, healthcare_company WHERE (ticket.amount - ticket.paid > 0)
